  "code": "---\ntitle: State of the art\n---\nstateDiagram-v2\n    Researcher&nbsp;or&nbsp;Data&nbsp;Scientist --> Python: write prototype\n    Researcher&nbsp;or&nbsp;Data&nbsp;Scientist --> Notebooks: write prototype\n    Researcher&nbsp;or&nbsp;Data&nbsp;Scientist --> R: write prototype\n    Python --> Software&nbsp;Engineer\n    R --> Software&nbsp;Engineer\n    Notebooks --> Software&nbsp;Engineer\n    Software&nbsp;Engineer --> Container: productize\n    Software&nbsp;Engineer --> Kubeflow&nbsp;Component: productize\n    Software&nbsp;Engineer --> Kubernetes&nbsp;Job: productize\n",
