  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张图来说明机器学习工作流从研究到生产的转化过程。核心想法是：研究人员先用Python、R或者Notebooks写原型，然后软件工程师把这些东西产品化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Researcher or Data Scientist",
        "Python",
        "R",
        "Notebooks",
        "Software Engineer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那产品化的具体形式有哪些？是统一成一个输出，还是可能有不同的部署形态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Software Engineer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "产品化有三种主要路径：可以打包成标准Container，也可以做成Kubeflow Component，或者直接部署为Kubernetes Job。这三种覆盖了从简单到复杂的不同场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Container",
        "Kubeflow Component",
        "Kubernetes Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画一版：左边是Researcher or Data Scientist，中间连到Python、R、Notebooks三个原型工具，然后汇总到Software Engineer，最后分出三条线到Container、Kubeflow Component和Kubernetes Job。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Researcher or Data Scientist",
        "Python",
        "R",
        "Notebooks",
        "Software Engineer",
        "Container",
        "Kubeflow Component",
        "Kubernetes Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构是对的，但关系标签需要补上——研究人员到三个工具都是\"write prototype\"，工程师到三个产品化目标都是\"productize\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "write prototype",
        "productize"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了关系标签。另外我注意到Notebooks和Python有重叠，但既然研究场景里有人直接用Python脚本、有人偏好Notebook环境，分开列出来更清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Python",
        "Notebooks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，而且R也要保留，有些统计团队坚持用R做原型。图的名字就叫\"State of the art\"吧，表示这是当前业界标准的流转模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title: State of the art",
        "R"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下最终结构：标题\"State of the art\"，Researcher or Data Scientist作为起点，通过write prototype连接到Python、R、Notebooks，三者都流向Software Engineer，再由productize关系分岔到Container、Kubeflow Component和Kubernetes Job。这样没问题我就定稿了。",
